type of session tracking .basic example of getParameter(), getWriter() (/books.html)

session
session tracking method-http session with url rewriting and cookies

hff
session tracking method- hidden form fields

scl
type of servlet listener-servletcontextlistener, getServletContext(), setAttribute(), getAttribute()

hsl
